caption: Always a pleasure when I visited the GSA Headquarters location of Which Wich. The staff was friendly and super professional. I stopped in so frequently that they automatically knew what I was ordering before I even gave them the marked up brown bag. Unfortunate that COVID-19 shut them down these last few months, which were my last in DC. Whenever I'm back in town, I'll definitely stop by.

They went above and beyond as usual! Even during these trying times this team made my work group and my year by stepping up and showing out! Sandwiches were delicious and whole setup was top-notch. I was the definitely the office HERO!!

Everything is optional. Which which offers a dizzying array of options. You basically check off your order on your bag. From bread type, size, meat toppings, condiments...everything. And they offer just about everything. Takes "have it your way" seriously.
